title: [2003] ATB The Dj In The Mix
description:
The DJ in the Mix is the debut compilation album by German DJ AndrÃ© Tanneberger, better known as ATB. The compilation includes 32 tracks of new and previously released trance from well-known international musicians in the genre, such as Paul van Dyk, Chicane, Armin van Buuren, Binary Finary, Woody van Eyden, 2 Trance, and ATB himself.
